<ul>
  <li>battery
 If the current is I, battery capacity is C, and discharge rate is D, then the instantaneous current draw is<code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">I = C X D</code></li>
</ul>

<blockquote>
  <p>5000mAh with discharging rate of 10C would be ` I = 5.0 x 10 = 50A`</p>
</blockquote>

